Description: # flask-sock
        WebSocket support for Flask
        
        ## Installation
        
        ```bash
        pip install flask-sock
        ```
        
        ## Example
        
        ```python
        from flask import Flask, render_template
        from flask_sock import Sock
        
        app = Flask(__name__)
        sock = Sock(app)
        
        
        @sock.route('/echo')
        def echo(sock):
            while True:
                data = sock.receive()
                sock.send(data)
        ```
        
